{"word":"G5302 - ὑστερέω - hysteréō - hoos-ter-eh'-o - Come behind","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑστερέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hysteréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoos-ter-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come behind</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - குறைவாயிரு, அற்றவர்களாயிரு, இழந்துபோ"},{"paragraph":"1. behind"},{"paragraph":"2. to suffer, want"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5306 - ὕστερος - hýsteros - hoos'-ter-os/5306\">G5306</a>; to <i>be later</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>be inferior</i>; genitively to <i>fall short</i> (<i>be deficient</i>): - come behind (short), be destitute, fall, lack, suffer need, (be in) want, be the worse.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5302/5302\">G5302</a>, <a href=\"#/G5303/5303\">G5303</a>, <a href=\"#/G5304/5304\">G5304</a>, <a href=\"#/G5305/5305\">G5305</a>, <a href=\"#/G5306/5306\">G5306</a>, <a href=\"#/G650/650\">G650</a>"}]}